<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>have the floor • take the floor</xh5><p> <i>have the floor—</i>speak at a meeting, in a debate, etc.: You now <u>have the floor</u> for the next five minutes.</p><p><i>take the floor—</i>1. <i>= have the floor: </i>Arthur was one of several House members to <u>take the floor</u>. 2. start dancing at a party, etc.: “Will you dance with me?” She got up and they <u>took the floor</u>.</p> </entry>
